com.here.android.mpa.common

Class MatchedGeoPosition

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.common.GeoPosition
      • com.here.android.mpa.common.MatchedGeoPosition

  • public final class MatchedGeoPosition
extends GeoPosition
    A extended GeoPosition class which provides additional position-related information. The class is designed to support walk or drive navigation.
    See Also:
    PositioningManager.isExtrapolated(), PositioningManager.OnPositionChangedListener.onPositionUpdated(PositioningManager.LocationMethod, GeoPosition, boolean)

      • getMatchQuality

        public int getMatchQuality()
        Returns a value indicating the quality of the given map-matched position object.
        Returns:
